bot_dtt_real-underground :

Context : Terrorist force have taken an underground-scientist-facility . They have one hostage . 

You , and your team need to release this hostage . In order to make it , you have to choose one of the five classes available : Sapper , Sniper , Assault , Reco and Support . This maps is based on a cooperation game-play , so take of your teamates . In this map , Real-Concept is activiated (real balistic damages) . The map is pre-configured , you just need to run it and join CT Force . In order to have a great game-play , you must a have 64 slot server .

www.dtt-creation.fr 

Enjoy !
